1.00	Uludag_University	UludaÄŸ University	Uludag University (Turkish: ) is a university located in Bursa, Turkey. The research and education conducted by the university have an emphasis on medicine, engineering, natural sciences and art. In particular, Faculty of Medicine and Mechanical Engineering Department have several well-reputed academicians in their organizations. The official language of instruction at Uludag University is Turkish.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/37/Uludag_University.jpg/130px-Uludag_University.jpg
